OL,6,FScherzinger, 46, was an X Factor judge
OL,7,Fwho mentored Liam Payne during his
OL,8,Ftime on the show, and helped to put
OL,9,Ftogether the band One Direction. ITV
OL,10,FNews' Sam Holder reports
OL,12,FNicole Scherzinger has paid tribute to
OL,13,Fformer X Factor mentee and Netflix co-
OL,14,Fstar Liam Payne, as it was revealed
OL,15,Fshe was in contact with him on the day
OL,16,Fhe died.
OL,18,FThe One Direction star died at the age
OL,19,Fof 31, after falling from a third-
OL,20,Ffloor balcony of a hotel in Buenos
OL,21,FAires last week.
