OL,6,FScherzinger, 46, was an X Factor judge
OL,7,Fwho mentored Liam Payne during his
OL,8,Ftime on the show and helped to put
OL,9,Ftogether the band One Direction.
OL,11,FShe was due to star alongside Payne
OL,12,Fand Destiny's Child singer Kelly
OL,13,FRowland in a new Netflix show
OL,14,F'Building the Band'.
OL,16,FFilming had reportedly wrapped just
OL,17,Fweeks before Payne's death.
