OL,3,CNicole Scherzinger, who texted Liam
OL,4,CPayne on the day he died, pays tribute
OL,6,FIn a post on Instagram on Friday,
OL,7,FScherzinger said she was grateful to
OL,8,Fhave known Payne's "sweet soul" and to
OL,9,Fhave had the chance to work with him.
OL,11,FShe is currently starring as Norma
OL,12,FDesmond in Andrew Lloyd Webber's
OL,13,Fmusical Sunset Boulevard.
OL,15,FThe composer said in an interview with
OL,16,FBillboard that Scherzinger still
OL,17,Fperformed on stage the night she found
OL,18,Fout Payne had died, and that he had
OL,19,Ftexted her that day.
