OL,3,CNicole Scherzinger, who texted Liam
OL,4,CPayne on the day he died, pays tribute
OL,6,FLloyd Webber said: "The fact that she
OL,7,Feven did the show at all is
OL,8,Fextraordinary. I mean she is an
OL,9,Famazing, amazing woman. She is without
OL,10,Fany question one of the finest
OL,11,Fperformers I've ever worked with."
OL,13,FIn an Instagram tribute, Scherzinger
OL,14,Fsaid: "Dear Liam, I will forever
OL,15,Fcherish and treasure the time we
OL,16,Fshared together, from 15 years ago
OL,17,Fwhen One Direction was born, right up
OL,18,Funtil just a few weeks ago.
